document.full_text: radioactive water appears to be leaking from a waste disposal building at japan's fukushima nuclear complex, operator tokyo electric power said on thursday, in a new setback to the battle to contain radiation from the crippled power plant.
document.title: new leak feared at stricken japan nuclear plant
